{"tid":983120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[新天龍八部] 史上最MK的王語嫣 - Janice Man","createTime":"2019-01-15T16:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T20:12:08.000Z","uid":12558,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2540c52db090c05c252ff1ec03e6d7a98c7dc84e","tid":983120,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"金庸名著《天龍八部》第6次拍成電視劇，而每一個版本，劇迷最關心的必然是誰人演出神仙姐姐王語嫣，而在去年10月宣佈由Janice Man(文詠珊)演出該角後，網民已經一面倒指她仙氣欠奉，莫說初代(1982)演出王語嫣的陳玉蓮，連之後的李若彤、劉亦菲亦遠遠比不上，近日JM的劇中造型曝光，確是一如所料，被指是史上最MK的王語嫣，破壞了劇迷的美好回憶。<br />\n<br />\n王語嫣是《天龍八部》的女主角，慕容復的表妹，雖然不懂武功，胸中武學知識卻相當淵博，而小說中三大男主角之一的段譽，在無量山崖的石洞中，見到一尊美女白玉雕像，驚為天人，更稱呼為「神仙姐姐」，之後初遇外貌一模一樣的王語嫣，隨即一見傾心，更一直稱對方是神仙姐姐，所以歷年演出王語嫣的女星，固然要靚到Dum一聲，最重要是具有出塵仙氣，在《新天龍八部》中由Janice Man演出王語嫣，仙氣欠奉，MK味濃，網民一面倒話要棄劇。<br />\n<br />\nJanice Man現年30歲，比起陳玉蓮22歲、張檬25歲、劉亦菲16歲時演出王語嫣，年紀明顯大了一截，與其說是神仙姐姐，更像是神仙媽媽。除此之外，王語嫣演出者往往也有份在另一齣金庸小說《神鵰俠侶》演出小龍女，包括陳玉蓮、李若彤及劉亦菲，無非是因為具有仙氣的女星十分罕有。至於Janice Man雖然也有演出內地古裝劇《蜀山戰紀之劍俠傳奇》及《九州海上牧雲記》，但跟王語嫣的氣質，始終有一段距離，至於演出會否帶來全新的王語嫣，劇迷要拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPs5EQx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPs5EQx.png&h=589d4246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRp4aXh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRp4aXh.png&h=2ea67b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peDgMvD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeDgMvD.png&h=de3093a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OS1YZQE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOS1YZQE.png&h=ad53b289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYXQQXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYXQQXk.png&h=0c81e2ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6z068J6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6z068J6.png&h=5c500f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnMx4hr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnMx4hr.png&h=fe1acbcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3ee2557bd505486c13c270774e67d117c83401c","tid":983120,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"值得一提既係,佢08年代言過gameone代理既天龍八部,分飾阿紫同阿朱"},{"pid":"9b635dc7a784fa83a91ae04a63869a6e58c35b2e","tid":983120,"uid":3501,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"e3ee2557bd505486c13c270774e67d117c83401c","tid":983120,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"值得一提既係,佢08年代言過gameone代理既天龍八部,分飾阿紫同阿朱"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aj8P6yo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faj8P6yo.png&h=57e0c6d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95cdbf5812f0bdeb7d79e548013d0d9cee9c5d4d","tid":983120,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b635dc7a784fa83a91ae04a63869a6e58c35b2e","tid":983120,"uid":3501,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"e3ee2557bd505486c13c270774e67d117c83401c","tid":983120,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"值得一提既係,佢08年代言過gameone代理既天龍八部,分飾阿紫同阿朱"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aj8P6yo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faj8P6yo.png&h=57e0c6d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"阿朱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab7c691b2117a863d8f5ffe1bdebb272e2b58d5","tid":983120,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"由選角得知一二呢套野垃圾劇居多"},{"pid":"ceefb852e291116c5e69e73952d59b5cb996297f","tid":983120,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T17:01:59.000Z","msg